  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, it's an area that was totally closed and all the Jews were kind of put in there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, it turns out that the ghetto [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was going to be way too small for all these people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that's one reason why they had this mass massacre at the cemetery for that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the ghetto was formed and the remaining Jews, which incidentally was more than 3,000 because they didn't find all the Jews taken to the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "For example, my stepfather-to-be later, he somehow escaped.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was in hiding and he never went to the cemetery, you see.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In our case, it was a little different.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because people-- when the Germans came to an apartment, they said, are there any Jews here?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Polish would always say-- in most cases, they would point towards the Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
